WELL SCHOOL is going good started trig..damn that class is hell... dont understand anything at all.... i think i am a dumbass or when i do trig it makes me think i am a dumbass cause i get all the answers wrong when i work them out.... i am doing fine in algebra 2, us history, and english 3......well like 7 more weeks of school left cant wait because i want it to be over so the summer will be here... i Need to start back running. get back to my healthy self.. well sorry so short i will update later tonight. i am out

well Saturday early early in the morning i leave for bham(birmingam)... gonna be fun... i will return on sunday...... then i have to go back to school on monday which really sucks.. startin the last 9 weeks of school That mean i get a new third block trig... hell.... well i am glad it will be the last nine weeks because that mean i will be senior hell yeah getting out of hight school in 2005.... cant wait....
i am tired of Ocean Springs High School and the People in it.....

was up was up.....
 

        well my life is gottin better now.... my weekend was awesome... friday i went of to parisa's house to watch her brother, cause they went out to eat... after they got back we talked for alittle while.. then they brought me home and i had to finish the damn history day thing.... didnt get finished till 3:30 in the morning... 


i got up at 5:30 to be at the school.. i get their and my teacher and two people are their so my teacher gets pissed off becuase two other were suppose to be at the school... they never showed up.. one of them was my partner... i was fuckin made because i stayed up till 3:30 to finish the damn thing, only get like an hour of sleep then i did all that for nothing.. so when i see my partner at school i am gonna say something to them... well i get a participation grade so thats cool.. free 100 hell yeah... then i go to tato nut and get some doughnuts..fuck yeah that place is the best... then i came home eat some doughnuts and then go back to bed then i get a phone call at 10:15 it was my dad calling from iraq to tell me he is coming home from iraq earlier then he is suppose to... he siad i am gonna be in georgia march 12 but i want be to mississippi tell april 15... i was so happy but still kinda sad cause i want see him till april 15, but aleast he will out of iraq.... 


saturday i did stuff with ashley hill it was fun.

today i went to a birthday party for my cousin he turned one 

well i am gonna go 

peace, 
jbush

havent updated in a while so i thought i would... well this week is going good so far.... Saturday i have to get up before the break of dawn to go to the history day competition at university of southern miss... If we win first or second we get to go to washington... os has never been to the history day thing... this is the first year so i hope we do good.... Biloxi always win so maybe we can beat them this year.... well life is going good... well april is coming up so fast i cant wait because my dad will be home from iraq... so excited... havent seen him in a year and 1 month is being along time away from a family member... gets to you....its been hard , but i have gotten through it..... well school is going good, i am just tired of algebra 2... cause it has gotten hard or the teacher doesnt know how to explain it very well... i had an 84 now i have a 77... i just need to study more and i will be able to pull my grade up.... so i need to quit shitting around an pull that grade up so i will have a good grade in that class.. i am doing good in my other classes 2 a's and 1 b... why cant my algebra 2 grade be a good grade..... i can wait till next weekend cause i get to go to birmingham... its gonna be fun... wont be here for a weekend cant wait, because i hate being here...well i dont know what else to type...i will think of something... well my sister is coming down from colorado to take my moms mustang because she is buying it.. now i wont have a car to drive... and my mom wont buy me a car because she has two motorcycles now..we have everything in the world but not justin a car.... which i want but will never get till i am 25.... haha... maybe not even 25... might be later then late...like 40... i get mad at my mom cause she wont buy me a car.. its not fair because everyones else's parents buy them and car and pay for then insurance and gas... why cant my mom be like that... i guess i will have to talk to my dad when he gets back and see if he will help me by a car... i think he will help me, because he is nice like that and thinks of his kids unlike someone else....just doesnt think about themselves and what they want.... he atleast buys other people stuff before he buys him self things... i want his truck he has, because he is suppose to be getting a f350, so maybe he will let me have his chevy... hell yeah that would be awesome... well i am out lata

JBUSH

Mardi gras was awesome.... went to the p'goula parade with rebecca, the diberville parade i was with shayna (rebecca's friend), rebecca and jeremy. then went to the biloxi parades...I stayed at the imperial palace on monday night it was alot of fun....then on tuesday morning got up and went to the palac and had breakfast, it was the best breakfast i have ever had... it was steak, eggs, toast, grits, and chocolate milk... i have never had such a good steak before. Then we went back to the imperial palace to move our stuff from the 13th floor to the 19th floor.. after that we went down to where we were gonna be at for the parades an i met up with rebecca and jeremy, we walked around and caught alot of stuff. Brandi made me a rebecca some drinks, they were really good. Then me, rebecca, and jeremy walked back to my room at the imperial palace, it was so far away. we got back before the second parade so we walked around somemore, then before the second parade started we went an stood by brandi... that parade sucked it always does.. After the second parade rebecca and jeremy were gonna leave, but rebecca called her mom and asked her an her mom had to talk to my aunt so she did and rebecca got to stay. I was glad cause i didnt wanna stand their by myself with out my friends. We got alot of stuff during the night parade.. rebecca got light up titties, and she got an unopened bag of beads.. then it started to rain alittle, but i didnt mind. Tuesday wore me out.. I was so tired when i went home.. i took a shower then called rebecca and talked to her for like 3 mins and then got off the phone with her and got a shower. After i got a shower i got on the computer got off around 11:00 and went to bed...

well i am out later,

JBUSH
